Template: gamemode/add_user_to_group
Type: note
Description: To enable Gamemode , users need to be added to the 'gamemode' user group.
 If this operation is not performed, some functions may not work properly.
 .
 You can add users to the 'gamemode' user group using the following command:
 .
 sudo usermod -aG gamemode <username>
 .
 Once added to a user group, you need to log out and back in for the changes to take effect.
Description-zh_CN.UTF-8: Gamemode 用户组配置要求
 要启用 Gamemode,需将用户添加到 'gamemode' 用户组。
 如果未进行此操作,部分功能可能无法正常使用
 .
 您可以使用以下命令将用户添加到 'gamemode' 用户组：
 .
 sudo usermod -aG gamemode <用户名>
 .
 添加用户到组,您需要注销并重新登录以使更改生效。
